'''Harold''' is a patient who came into the ER after the bus he was on was in an accident.

==History==
Harold was on a bus on the way to a cruise when it was in an accident. He said he wasn't surprised as the driver kept checking his phone. [[Fran (Season 12)|Fran]] said that he must have been watching porn with as intently as he'd been looking at his phone.
